name: Blocksmith Labs Forge
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: $FORGE is a utility token created by Blocksmith Labs. Holding and staking a Blocksmith Lab NFT allows users to earn a certain amount of $FORGE per month. $FORGE can be spent on a variety of things such as raffle and auctions for whitelist spots for NFT projects, NFTs themselves and other tangible items.
